data.description: Investors - get in now before the Brookland Manor redevelopment project raises property values!    The Mid City Redevelopment Project is approved for up to 1,800 residential units and 181,000 square feet of commercial space   This 3 bed 1.5 bath end unit is available now. At nearly 1600 total square feet, you don’t want to miss your opportunity to secure a property in an increasingly coveted area as major investment comes to the area.  Double pane vinyl windows, roof solar panels and Central air and heat already installed!  Bonus being on a tree lined street at the end of the row.         Currently owner-occupied, showings must be accompanied by listing agent with prior approval per seller.
